videos.description: Zion catches the back end of an alley-oop that he throws down with authority at Madison Square Garden.
videos.headline: Zion throws down thundering dunk

videos.description: Javin DeLaurier grabs a strong offensive rebound and gets the putback for a big Duke and-1 in the first half.
videos.headline: DeLaurier gets big and-1

videos.description: Zion Williamson gets up for another monster dunk late in the first half vs. No. 12 Texas Tech.
videos.headline: Zion throws down another monster dunk

videos.description: Jarrett Culver takes the ball to the hole and gets fouled on the big drive for Texas Tech against Duke.
videos.headline: Culver drives in the paint against Duke

videos.description: Norense Odiase fights for the big Texas Tech and-1 and flexes his muscles after the basket.
videos.headline: Odiase fights for and-1

videos.description: Jarrett Culver drives 1-on-1 and throws down a two-handed slam to get Madison Square Garden hyped.
videos.headline: Culver throws down big dunk

videos.description: Zion Williamson receives an offensive foul, his fifth overall, and fouls out of the game vs. Texas Tech.
videos.headline: Zion fouls out with under 4 minutes to go

videos.description: Cam Reddish drains a wide-open 3 from the corner as the crowd goes wild in the second half.
videos.headline: Reddish drains big 3 from corner

videos.description: Duke gets 33 points combined from RJ Barrett and Zion Williamson as they pull away from No. 12 Texas Tech in the second half on their way to a 69-58 victory.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Williamson, Barrett carry Duke past Texas Tech) 2018/12/20 ESHEET SOTFULL
